;; TEST-ID: tests.codegen.rt-path-literal-value
;; TEST-CONTEXT: monadc.context.reader.path-literals, monadc.context.language.path-values, monadc.context.tests.heap-path-regressions
;; TEST-PURPOSE: Verify syntactically valid Unix path literals compile as Path values.
;; TEST-ATOM: A home-relative Unix path literal in a define infers Path and show prints the path text.
